---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Specialty Work — Frye's Printing" description="Hot foil stamping, embossing, and die cutting on our three in-house Kluge presses. Premium finishes in Napa Valley.">
  <section class="bg-navy text-white py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <a href="/services" class="text-gold text-sm font-medium hover:text-gold-light transition-colors">&larr; All Services</a>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold mt-4">Specialty Work</h1>
      <p class="text-white/70 text-lg mt-4 max-w-2xl">
        Hot foil stamping, embossing, and die cutting — all done in-house on our three Kluge presses. Premium finishes most shops have to outsource.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-16">
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-8">
          
          <!-- Kluge Highlight -->
          <div class="bg-navy rounded-xl p-8 text-white">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Three Kluge Presses — In-House</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
              <p>
                This is where we really stand apart. We have <strong class="text-gold">three Kluge letterpresses</strong> dedicated to hot foil stamping, embossing, and die cutting. Most shops outsource this work — we do it all right here.
              </p>
              <p>
                That means faster turnaround on specialty finishing, tighter quality control, and the ability to do press checks on your foil stamping and embossing jobs without leaving Napa. For wineries, luxury brands, and anyone who wants their printed piece to make a lasting impression, this capability is a game-changer.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Three Services Grid -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-warm-gray rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gold/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z"/></svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy mb-2">Hot Foil Stamping</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-light text-sm">Gold, silver, copper, and custom foils for a luxurious metallic finish</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-warm-gray rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gold/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01"/></svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy mb-2">Embossing</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-light text-sm">Raised and debossed impressions that add dimension and tactile appeal</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-warm-gray rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gold/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.121 14.121L19 19m-7-7l7-7m-7 7l-2.879 2.879M12 12L9.121 9.121m0 5.758a3 3 0 10-4.243 4.243 3 3 0 004.243-4.243zm0-5.758a3 3 0 10-4.243-4.243 3 3 0 004.243 4.243z"/></svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy mb-2">Die Cutting</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-light text-sm">Custom shapes and precision cuts for unique, standout pieces</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Hot Foil Stamping</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-charcoal-light leading-relaxed">
              <p>
                Hot foil stamping uses heat and pressure to apply metallic or pigmented foil to paper, creating a brilliant, eye-catching finish. It's the hallmark of luxury printing — from wine labels and business cards to invitations and packaging.
              </p>
              <p>
                We offer a wide range of foil colors including gold, silver, copper, rose gold, and custom colors. The result is a finish that catches the light and demands attention.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Embossing &amp; Debossing</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-charcoal-light leading-relaxed">
              <p>
                Embossing raises an image or text above the surface of the paper, while debossing presses it below. Both techniques add a tactile dimension that makes printed pieces more memorable and engaging.
              </p>
              <p>
                Combined with foil stamping, embossing creates stunning multi-level effects that elevate your brand. It's perfect for logos, monograms, and key design elements you want people to feel as well as see.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Die Cutting</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-charcoal-light leading-relaxed">
              <p>
                Die cutting uses custom steel dies to cut paper into any shape you can imagine. From simple rounded corners to intricate custom shapes, die cutting lets you break free from the standard rectangle.
              </p>
              <p>
                Popular applications include custom-shaped business cards, unique packaging, pocket folders with custom pockets, and promotional pieces that stand out from the crowd.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Why Specialty Work at Frye's?</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-charcoal-light leading-relaxed">
              <p>
                <strong class="text-navy">Three Kluges, zero outsourcing.</strong> We have three Kluge letterpresses dedicated to specialty work. That means no waiting on outside vendors and no surprises.
              </p>
              <p>
                <strong class="text-navy">Local press checks.</strong> You can approve your foil stamping and embossing jobs right here in Napa — not hours away at some specialty shop.
              </p>
              <p>
                <strong class="text-navy">Seamless integration.</strong> Because we print and finish under one roof, your job moves smoothly from press to specialty finishing without delays or handoff issues.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Perfect For</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
              {['Wine Labels & Packaging', 'Business Cards', 'Invitations & Announcements', 'Certificates & Awards', 'Pocket Folders', 'Luxury Packaging', 'Stationery & Letterhead', 'Marketing Materials'].map((item) => (
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-charcoal-light">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                  {item}
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-warm-gray rounded-xl p-6 sticky top-28">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-navy mb-4">Get a Quote</h3>
            <p class="text-charcoal-light text-sm mb-5">
              Ready to add some premium finishing to your next project? Let's talk.
            </p>
            <a href="/quote" class="block w-full px-6 py-3 bg-terracotta text-white text-center font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-terracotta-light transition-colors">
              Request a Quote
            </a>
            <p class="text-charcoal-light text-xs mt-4 text-center">
              Or call <a href="tel:707-253-1114" class="text-terracotta hover:text-terracotta-light">(707) 253-1114</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
